_sText:
This is one of my best prefabs it is a teleporter which has four rotating disks which spin when the button is pressed.

The walkway in this has multiple spotlights set up along it to give a futuristic style.

You will need to create your own info_target which is the destination that you will appear at once teleported. 

(this may be appearing in an up-coming RP map of mine.)

If you are going to use this in a public map please PM me the link and/or server that it will be played on.

All feedback is welcomed.

!!Please Vote!!
